{"tid":1917352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家比狗逗或者被塔前，會唔會暫時除罩好啲？","createTime":"2020-03-09T12:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T01:59:14.000Z","uid":299530,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"206ceabddd3640659626fecfebb908e8bfe24698","tid":1917352,"uid":299530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T12:34:11.000Z","msg":"尋日大埔同將軍澳有好多手足被捕，同埋啲狗呢排興係條街無聲無息地咬手足。<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候認人就好重要，相信大家都有去被捕關注組tg認人。但我發覺被捕手足嘅相有一半都係戴住口戴，令到認人困難左。<br />\n<br />\n個人認為大家比狗逗開始或者一見有鏡頭影住自己，就應該除口罩，問完話先戴翻。係街電光石火下被咬都要盡可能除罩，望到有人影相拍片立即嗌自己個名。<br />\n<br />\n有時淨係有名未必足夠，有埋樣或者可以增加自己比人認到個可能性。命仔要緊啊大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪一個好建議。或者冇呢個必要？或者除左可能反而有壞處？ 歡迎大家討論下"},{"pid":"bdbdc63d562fa4030db99b59aa6800e8c87cbfb8","tid":1917352,"uid":299530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T12:36:55.000Z","msg":"推啊推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48989abc5acee8ecc0236f9ba1b5833fa1299157","tid":1917352,"uid":299530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T12:37:34.000Z","msg":"入黎講下你嘅睇法"},{"pid":"36f627697f826e996f0293458dfaddc7a2cfc0d3","tid":1917352,"uid":299530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T12:38:23.000Z","msg":"希望手足被消失嘅機會減少"},{"pid":"f0a8117ba02ec4cc33a869cc07bae1fc73349785","tid":1917352,"uid":299530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T12:49:03.000Z","msg":"hi <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f78f1bfc98d7862d6cbea74377121d7aadd911c","tid":1917352,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:34:55.000Z","msg":"問題是病毒點算"},{"pid":"f15d50407e23535e8efe688bf81861b4efd6d2fc","tid":1917352,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:41:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/